---
title: Vote Casting — Sequence Diagram
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant V as Voter
    participant UI as Frontend
    participant API as Express API
    participant SC as Smart Contract
    participant SE as Sync Engine
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    V->>UI: Connect MetaMask wallet
    UI->>API: GET /api/voters/me?wallet=0x...
    API-->>UI: Voter status (eligible)
    
    V->>UI: Select President, Secretary, GMs (up to 5)
    V->>UI: Click "Cast Vote"
    UI->>API: GET /api/voters/proof?wallet=0x...
    API-->>UI: Merkle proof array
    
    UI->>SC: castVote(presId, secId, gmIds, proof)
    SC->>SC: Verify Merkle proof
    SC->>SC: Validate female GM count (≥2)
    SC->>SC: Record vote counts
    SC-->>UI: Transaction receipt (BallotCast event)
    
    par Live sync
        SE->>SC: Poll for VoteCast events
        SC-->>SE: BallotCast log
        SE->>DB: UPDATE vote_count
        SE-->>UI: Socket.IO voteUpdate
    end
    
    UI-->>V: Updated results displayed
